35
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:26,070
And also we have order fulfillment asynchronous case.

36
00:02:26,070 --> 00:02:32,820
This will be perform order fulfillment operations like billing shipment notification with raising the

37
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:36,330
