40
00:02:47,370 --> 00:02:52,950
Here you can see the table including the Http get, post, put and delete methods.

41
00:02:52,950 --> 00:02:59,130
We will basically perform these use cases, which is the slash orders, get order with pagination and

42
00:02:59,130 --> 00:02:59,910
