43
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:01,020
Slash order name.

44
00:03:01,020 --> 00:03:07,770
We will get orders by order name filter by the order name, and after that we can filter by the customer

45
00:03:07,770 --> 00:03:12,720
ID including the orders slash customer slash customer ID end point.

46
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:19,350
And after that we will perform http post, put and delete operation in order to perform Crud operations

47
00:03:19,350 --> 00:03:20,730
