50
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:38,130
And the last analyzing is infrastructure data underlying data structure of the ordering microservices.

51
00:03:38,130 --> 00:03:45,420
So we can say that ordering microservice has one data store which is the SQL server relational databases.

52
00:03:45,420 --> 00:03:52,200
So that means we basically use relational database SQL server used for the storing orders and order

53
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:52,830
